               <msContents>
                  <summary>Fragment of an Amharic Prayerbook</summary>
                     <textLang mainLang="am">Amharic</textLang>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="8v" facs="001">Fols 1r–8v</locus><title>Fragment of an Amharic prayerbook, translated from Gǝ‘ǝz, divided into chapters</title>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="1r" facs="001">Fols 1r and following</locus><title>Chapter Three, section three</title><incipit xml:lang="am">ምዕራፍ፡ ፫፡ ክፍል፡ ፫፡ መምሬ፡ ሆይ፡ ጌታዬ፡ ሆይ፡ ፈጣሪ፡ ሆይ፡ እለምንሃለሁ፡ ከኃጢአቴ፡ ባሕር፡ ማዕበል፡ ታድነኝ፡ ዘንድ፡ ከመሰናክሌም፡...</incipit></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from="3r" facs="003">Fols 3r and following</locus><title>Chapter Two, section two</title><incipit xml:lang="am">ምዕራፍ፡ ፪፡ ክፍል ፪ኛ፡ ሰውን የፈጠርክ ሆይ በወሰንከው፡ ሥርዓት፡ ከፊትሕ፡ እቆም፡ ዘንድ፡ አድነኝ፡ ነፍስን፡ የተከልክ፡ አጽቆችን፡ ያለመለምክ::...</incipit></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3"><locus from="5r" facs="005">Fols 5r and following</locus><title>Chapter Five, section five</title><incipit xml:lang="am">ምዕራፍ፡ ፭፡ ክፍል፡ ፭፡ ጌታየ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሆይ፡ የጠፉትን ፈልገህ፡ ከቦታቸው፡ ልታገባ፡ ልትመለስ፡ የመጣህ፡ አንተ፡ ነህ፡...</incipit></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4"><locus from="7r" facs="007">Fols 7r and following</locus><title>Chapter Four, section four</title><incipit xml:lang="am">ምዕራፍ፡ ፬፡ ክፍል፡ ፬፡ የተባረኩ፡ የደቀ፡ መዛሙርቶችህን፡ ዕውቀት፡ እንደገለጽሕ፡ የአምላካዊ፡ ቃልንም፡ ትርጓሜ፡ አውቀው፡ ወደማትመረመር፡ መለኮትህ፡ ዕውቀት፡ እንደተመለሱ:... </incipit></msItem>
                  </msItem>
